# Trash Kit Monorepo Structure

This is a pnpm workspace monorepo containing three main packages:

## Package Structure
- **@trash-kit/ui**: React UI components library
- **@trash-kit/common**: Shared utilities, hooks, and types
- **@trash-kit/auth**: Authentication library and services
- **example**: Next.js example application

## Key Files
- [package.json](mdc:package.json) - Root package configuration with workspace scripts
- [pnpm-workspace.yaml](mdc:pnpm-workspace.yaml) - Workspace configuration
- [biome.json](mdc:biome.json) - Linting and formatting configuration

## Package Dependencies
- UI and Auth packages depend on Common package
- All packages use workspace references: `"@trash-kit/common": "workspace:*"`

## Development Commands
- `pnpm dev` - Runs all packages in parallel
- `pnpm build` - Builds all packages in parallel
- `pnpm release:ui` - Releases UI package only
- `pnpm release:common` - Releases Common package only
- `pnpm release:auth` - Releases Auth package only
- `pnpm release:all` - Releases all packages

## Release System
- Uses semantic-release with separate `.releaserc.json` files per package
- GitHub Actions workflows for automated releases
- Conventional commits for version management